snippet.title: Tux and Fanny - video game trailer
snippet.description:
Here is the trailer for the Tux and Fanny video game, coming September 9th to Nintendo Switch, Windows, Mac and Linux systems. Stay tuned for updates!

itch page here: https://ghosttime.itch.io/tux-and-fanny
nintendo switch page here: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/tux-and-fanny-switch/
